XYZ2PNG
=======

XYZ2PNG is a small tool to convert RPG Maker 2000 and 2003 XYZ image
file format into PNG images.

XYZ2PNG is part of the EasyRPG Project. More information is available
at the project website:

  https://easy-rpg.org/


Documentation
-------------

Documentation is available at the documentation wiki:

  https://easy-rpg.org/wiki/


Requirements
------------

libpng


Source code
-----------

XYZ2PNG development is hosted by GitHub.
Project files are available in Git repositories.

  https://github.com/EasyRPG/Tools


Building
--------

Run:

  make



License
-------

XYZ2PNG is free software. See the file COPYING for copying conditions.
